---
import { Instagram, Facebook } from "lucide-astro";
---

<footer id="contatti" class="bg-bg-dark text-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-[1200px] mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10">
        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-12 border-b border-white/10 pb-12"
        >
            <div class="col-span-1 md:col-span-1 space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
                    <img
                        src="/icon.svg"
                        alt="Osteria Cilea Logo"
                        class="size-12"
                    />
                </div>
                <p class="text-white/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">
                    L'autentica cucina siciliana nel cuore di Palermo.
                    Tradizione, passione e sapori di famiglia in ogni boccone.
                </p>
                <div class="flex gap-4">
                    <a
                        href="https://www.instagram.com/osteriacilea/"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="p-2 bg-white/5 hover:bg-primary transition-colors rounded-full"
                    >
                        <Instagram class="w-5 h-5" />
                    </a>
                    <a
                        href="https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61585332472816"
                        target="_blank"
                        class="p-2 bg-white/5 hover:bg-primary transition-colors rounded-full"
                    >
                        <Facebook class="w-5 h-5" />
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4
                    class="font-bold mb-6 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-primary"
                >
                    Orari
                </h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-white/60 space-y-2">
                    <li>Lunedì - Domenica:</li>
                    <li>12:30 - 15:00 / 19:30 - 23:00</li>
                    <li class="text-primary font-bold">Martedì: Chiuso</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4
                    class="font-bold mb-6 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-primary"
                >
                    Contatti
                </h4>
                <ul class="text-sm text-white/60 space-y-2">
                    <li>Via Francesco Cilea, 79</li>
                    <li>90144 Palermo, Italia</li>
                    <li>
                        <a
                            href="tel:+393925922651"
                            class="hover:text-primary transition-colors"
                            >+39 392 592 2651</a
                        >
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h4
                    class="font-bold mb-6 uppercase text-xs tracking-widest text-primary"
                >
                    Dove Siamo
                </h4>
                <div
                    class="w-full h-32 bg-white/10 rounded-lg overflow-hidden grayscale contrast-125 opacity-70 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                >
                    <iframe
                        src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3138.174243457939!2d13.335098976449691!3d38.13614119126085!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x1319efc9e2352cb7%3A0xd32e5be26e55aa0f!2sOsteria%20Cilea!5e0!3m2!1sit!2sit!4v1769986910173!5m2!1sit!2sit"
                        width="100%"
                        height="100%"
                        style="border:0;"
                        allowfullscreen=""
                        loading="lazy"
                        referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div
            class="pt-8 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4 text-xs text-white/40"
        >
            <p>
                © {new Date().getFullYear()} Osteria Cilea. Tutti i diritti riservati.
            </p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 group">
                    <span class="opacity-50">Developed by</span>
                    <a
                        href="https://gofoodmenu.it"
                        target="_blank"
                        rel="noopener noreferrer"
                        class="flex items-center gap-1.5 hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity"
                    >
                        <img
                            src="/gofood.svg"
                            alt="GO!Food Italia"
                            class="h-4 w-auto"
                        />
                    </a>
                </div>
                <div class="h-3 w-[1px] bg-white/10 hidden md:block"></div>
                <div class="flex gap-6">
                    <a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#"
                        >Privacy Policy</a
                    >
                    <a class="hover:text-primary transition-colors" href="#"
                        >Termini e Condizioni</a
                    >
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
